=== Teragen ===
Generates random data to sort. The first argument is '''number of 100-byte rows''', so for 1TB you put in '''10,000,000,000'''
 hadoop jar /usr/share/hadoop/hadoop-examples-1.0.3.jar teragen 10000000000 /user/hdfs/terasort-input

=== Terasort ===
Actually sort it.
 hadoop jar /usr/share/hadoop/hadoop-examples-1.0.3.jar terasort /user/hduser/terasort-input /user/hdfs/terasort-output

=== Teravalidate ===
Check that the sort actually worked correctly.
 hadoop jar /usr/share/hadoop/hadoop-examples-1.0.3.jar teravalidate /user/hduser/terasort-output /user/hdfs/terasort-validate

